{
  "id": "RAW_90c980be",
  "title": "小红书 MySQL 内核秒杀能力重磅再升级",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4OTc2MzczNg==&mid=2247494557&idx=1&sn=9dba41e4eb80a5386f2cca70666c7c23",
  "date": "2026-01-19 10:04:00",
  "author": "小红书技术REDtech",
  "siteName": "小红书技术REDtech",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);text-align: justify;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“秒杀”是电商平台最典型的高并发促销场景，双十一等大促活动也常以秒杀能力作为数据库技术实力的标志。随着小红书电商业务快速增长，直播带货等爆品场景对极致下单速度的需求更加突出，希望将下单吞吐提升至 1W+/s。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 MySQL 内核实现的合并秒杀优化，相对排队秒杀方案，将秒杀写入能力再提升 5 倍，相对MySQL 社区版本更有百倍的性能提升。在设计上保持了和排队秒杀一致的能力，该能力对业务完全透明：仅需升级 MySQL 内核，无需改动 SQL，即可获得 5 倍以上性能提升。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">该方案不仅显著提升库存、优惠券、红包等高抢购场景的用户体验，也能在热门笔记点赞等高频写入场景实现数量级性能增强。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=190d4761&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmotrFqjqSPknQNqOPxMsXL7h9sxWFRiaf46wfIq15paFsz0zyOHukGyeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">24年小红书数据库团队首次通过对热点线程排队，将自研版本秒杀性能提升了10倍，但依然跟不上业务的快速发展。尤其是在直播带货、热门笔记点赞、爆品抢购等场景下，业务迫切需要更快的秒杀速度，本次数据库团队在自研内核上迭代实现了合并秒杀方案，将热点行更新速度提升5倍至1.5W/s+，极大提升了用户的使用体验。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010851\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb9afecd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoyDicOSOfW2nIvs9CIfMhj1YNmXy4Z84odvd1jmY5Vxh4zlKNic1Sw5Mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并秒杀版本在方案设计时考虑了和排队版本的兼容性，内核会根据SQL自动选择最优的秒杀方案。对于热点SQL，内核会依据SQL自动选择合并秒杀、排队秒杀和普通更新的最优解，只需升级MySQL内核版本，无需业务侧修改SQL即可享受到</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">5倍以上</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的性能提升。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从下面性能分析图可以看到，在128线程秒杀时，TPS从4276提升至23543，提升约</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">5.5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">倍。在1024线程极端场景下，仍然有4.7倍性能提升。随着线程数的升高，线程切换的开销越来越大，TPS也逐步下降，因此建议线程数保持在128-256之间以获得最佳性能。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4064815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010853\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66eb2444&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoYLIsqkoFT0rELr0UNxT6fE4fNLkylDRT1HiaeiawvxHYGQ7jyuaBHvXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试数据均为sysbench模拟标准库存扣减模型进行的压测数据。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8ad6ccd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmovE5kLB4J0FaCmrkqBWjpGf4cXghtBeYoJx3OPzY8CJmb7nwZJtUpibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先对秒杀场景进行分析，抽象出了它的事务模型。下面所示为最经典的库存扣减模型：</span></p>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);text-align: justify;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">begin;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">insert into inventory_log value (...);</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">-- 插入库存修改的流水表</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">update inventory set quantity=quantity-1 where sku_id=? and quantity &gt; 0; &nbsp;</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">-- 扣减库存表</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">commit;</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着并发数的增加，数据库的update写入性能急剧下降，最终基本处于不可用的状态（TPS约为100-200），出现非常严重的卡顿，下面将依次分析不同方案的性能瓶颈点和解决思路。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.1 排队</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒杀提升点</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并秒杀版本重点解决了性能下降问题，将秒杀性能维持在一个性能基本不变的状态。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 200%;overflow-x: hidden;max-width: 200% !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7097844112769486\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1206\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"100010877\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73ae2181&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoGsoITKthicGibh28rka9d95ULoZLOvbPiansK6KypEVRKtqHqEJzwicyibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6892561983471074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1210\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo5euo0RHYqiaPADg6Q0KFLDaKlXGlPY5pF8liaMjhPib1iaKbfMrvjBuXNg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1210\" data-cropy2=\"834.8566308243728\" data-backw=\"558\" data-backh=\"384\" data-imgfileid=\"100010897\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80b1ccfa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoRevThO4YEfHvFvY6AKzx2dWWH963ylneYPkBoR47ibYFXFDOp7Kr0fA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.2 合并</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒杀提升点</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">再次分析上面的库存扣减模型，每个事务都是（begin；insert；update；commit）这种格式。那么insert是插入不同的行（主键不一样），所以可以并发，但是update是对同一行的改写，无法并发，红色的标识为临界区（行锁）。所以性能的瓶颈点在update同一行的修改上，秒杀V2将解决该瓶颈点。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 200%;overflow-x: hidden;max-width: 200% !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9121212121212121\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"990\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo6wZPI1Mibzt07MhWgf6EwlgYpuXrhKyRC9IZZFcTbkWFLrhib5icwribyQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"990\" data-cropy2=\"903.0645161290323\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"494\" data-imgfileid=\"100010886\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b0b7dd3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoyeib2Bwty7AQCE1PgwZgR1f7hzBUlUMQ0srU8TmYPI2fuLOW8xOIoNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;margin: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9134808853118712\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"994\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"495\" data-imgfileid=\"100010887\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=88f93280&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo02jN8H09iazvnibAKNic4iclt5JCSmaEGVGniaUiajTFmweY69Q3DsJqQ1vg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.3 方案总结</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">将上述方案的瓶颈点和解决思路整合如下对比所示，直观反映了各方案的优化思路。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 300%;overflow-x: hidden;max-width: 300% !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 33.3333%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\