0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.117283950617284\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"648\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"606\" data-imgfileid=\"100010892\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94859e85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmozuMOckzYwBLbYnibVTDTSic2y03stmlmke5PK9ZekWA8tiaQwmlJ2WgoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010860\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e4cb223&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo0ZnU920eHkWteUrXbcBHia9JkVepOgcdPEhp0okWu1KbqaKDia50TgOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并秒杀将多个事务 SQL 合并到一个事务进行提交，修改了MySQL的事务模型，必然涉及到MySQL事务系统、锁系统、Binlog系统等模块的修改。合并秒杀方案提供了如下优势：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">生态组件无感知：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">将改动内容收敛到MySQL内核，输出的 Binlog内容和格式没有变化，对于DTS/Canel等组件无感知，避免了联动组件升级</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">内核升级无感知：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">不修改InnoDB格式，不影响版本兼容性和版本回退</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">业务SQL无修改：</span>和排队秒杀版本SQL语法兼容，可以动态开关。业务/DBA可以随时将合并秒杀退化到排队秒杀，也可以随时开启。可以同时将合并秒杀，排队秒杀，无秒杀在一个数据库同时跑起来，减少业务迁移成本。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2833333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100010899\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7d85759&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoqPQss9nUDibrsEgAT2QdpjN0tVsX0Thysyt0jlhMXjV8VjGibAItibtcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">一句话总结本方案：</span>合并秒杀通过Leader预读取库存数据写入缓存，在缓存中进行Follower库存数据合并扣减，最后Leader一次性将合并数据写入存储引擎，提升了写入性能。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.1 缓存可见性</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了合并秒杀，要解决如下两个问题：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据的可见性：目前MySQL的数据是线程可见的，这样最方便。但是合并秒杀是需要多个线程之间共享数据的。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据一致性问题：Leader-Follower的数据同步问题，要做好状态的流转。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.1.1 数据可见性</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了解决以上问题，按照表维度添加了全局缓存，多个线程操作同一张表的结构体访问同一份缓存，缓存的生命周期和表结构是一样的，方便缓存管理。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.162963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010861\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37f7cbbe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo0f6wJicxlNlF7PwoI01Lwe7utFyGSuHib2l6fvUtMZQysSSBV7VOfZTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.1.2 数据一致性</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">解决了数据的可见性问题，剩下的核心点就是解决Leader-Follower的数据同步问题，保证数据的一致性。下面一张图系统的展示了一个Leader两个Follower线程是如何配合扣减三次的：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先三个客户端发送了相同的update语句。经过了Queue PK，由于开启了合并秒杀，跳过了排队秒杀过程</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">三个线程开始抢独占锁，最先抢到的将自己标记为Leader，然后读取InnoDB数据和更新数据，将修改后的数据写入全局缓存。Leader做完了工作，释放独占锁，开始进入收集状态，等待若干毫秒</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外两个Follower开始抢独占锁。抢到的标记为Follower，然后将全局缓存数据写入线程缓存，然后更新线程缓存完成扣减，最后将线程缓存数据再写入全局缓存。释放独占锁，进入等待唤醒状态。在全局缓存中完成Follower的库存扣减</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">后面的线程依次进入Follower过程，按照读全局缓存-&gt;完成扣减-&gt;更新全局缓存的过程，依次执行了update语句扣减</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Leader线程完成了收集，重新申请独占锁，将全局缓存数据作为本组最终扣减的值。开始进入2PC过程完成最终数据提交。Leader完成后会唤醒Follower，所有SQL结束</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.9479905\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010863\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a7dca68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo4fZNTGlXARBRB752fJ74AIVoNEXYpdUTVyickwn4vK9AfeHv2nKWjsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.2 行</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">锁极致优化</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上面的过程看起来配合的非常好，是否还有优化空间？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">再次回到下面的这张图，将update分为两个步骤，一个是收集更新缓存阶段（phase 1），一个是commit阶段（phase 2）。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010867\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f1ddd60&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo6spibvO7tu9vSQoQrv6icH8BO16grW0CS6GXH0E13UfiaRQvpcFdJyXWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果将多个组提交按照时间串起来，可以看到上一个组必须commit完释放了行锁，才能让下一个组重新申请行锁。如下图所示。所以整个流水线在组内是合并提交的，但是组和组之间是完全的串行。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2675926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010868\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2df49fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoyoGBEDUq2KUCLTWcXhibiahGA0UN6VANvrT72msiaYISta5I8Q1IRebBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如按照两个阶段分为两个组，那么在第一个组进行commit的时候，第二个组完全可以开始收集，无需等待第一组commit完成。这样整体的执行时间会进一步压缩。以两个组为例，第一个组从1000扣减50为950，那么在第一个组提交950的时候，第二个组可以从950开始扣减。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如下图所示，绿色部分就是节省的时间。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3935185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010869\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c4eb88c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoKCcmTxwyZiadjAd2TwNwGibc5hXqrD2uUS2LqbYIHSkm9IYiboQ77vLXQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.3 Binlog并行提交</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个组的Binlog是同一批由Leader统一提交。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100010903\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9cc9c9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoId2Q9WQWOTkKFOkicJfPMPcibqrVmvNfLjT5xrZ4oTIQYr8aChTBgVLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.4 Crash Recovery优化</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Crash Recovery过程简单来说，先由Binlog生成一个事务集合，然后拿到Redolog进行对比，该提交就提交，该回滚就回滚。</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并秒杀是Leader提交Binlog，将整个组的Binlog都写入</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Redolog记录的是合并前后的值（例如1000-&gt;900)，但是binlog记录的是每个事务的改动（1000-&gt;999, 999-&gt;998)。所以要回滚Redolog的内容或者提交Redolog的内容，必须要求整个Binlog组的完整性</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 200%;overflow-x: hidden;max-width: 200% !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7004048582995951\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"988\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"380\" data-imgfileid=\"100010893\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b874062&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoU5tpNIP4XP7RDQFRhRRSOZXkOBcNQaU3f5blDLhRTukf88MMdKRdQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6787878787878788\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"990\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmo5oUic3sXVDz9DXtrPcnAnibEqTxHLnfzxuEST79IphQhJwrHkp1aDWEQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"990\" data-cropy2=\"672.4193548387098\" data-backw=\"558\" data-backh=\"379\" data-imgfileid=\"100010894\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3b1f19bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoCWYIBRXcdInfkPosqu75KzEmYibSSk1GXaxKvHoCT5naJYqoyUCM20g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0.5px; padding: 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">左右滑动查看</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于以上两种场景，Crash Recovery需要做好兼容处理。具体的思路如下:</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010874\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d4ce9c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoyrRfxoHfKqmxv5fSNsxatia34qJeb0MDNZPA6C5rHY33dwEJFDaGnkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">以数据组为单位进行扣减数据的提交和回滚，相对事务粒度更大一些。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010870\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=407d1466&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoibRdvazzxyfUXcHKvWxtvfW2SYdU4nuyGGHGYAxiboIPge6cjtPrYJbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">正如上面所述，在内核中使用的Hint关键字如下：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100010908\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3256fbcd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmoSN4B7ZaGjuy7l95dib5BomU6byUoDA86BZbEPX2XOnIqYElicQjraCfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6620370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100010901\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5d6bca7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86IvFM3AhYOrsF3c9cgibVZLmokPMp2oHDmQd3z76ngGSk4td0yWucpevq9KgbszJd0EBmEC7nR4aPNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">致谢</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">感谢阿里云RDS团队在方案中的技术支持，并在关键问题定位与优化建议方面提供了帮助。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2009259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010872\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=195e211f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_pn